{"id":9559,"type":2,"name":"妖精ディック","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/7c/99/9559_136eF.jpg","rating":{"total":13,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":1,"7":4,"8":4,"9":2,"10":1},"score":7.6},"summary":"《小鬼迪克》动画原名《妖精ディック》 ，由日本瑞鹰公司于1992年制作，故事内容改编自英国小说家Katharine M. Briggs的小说原作《Hobberdy Dick》它讲述了英国一个守护老房子的守屋精灵——迪克，为了保护主人的冒险故事。在20世纪九十年代中期引进中国，通过小神龙俱乐部及熊猫俱乐部与国内各个合作媒体的播放，掀起了一股“房宅精灵”的热潮，深深的影响了一代人。作品的画面唯美，音乐动听，故事情节设定自然流畅，最重要的是加入了以小鬼迪克为代表的精灵们，让孩子们的想象力得到了极大的提高。可惜不知什么原因，动画片结局一直没有正式播出，令广大观众留下了深深的遗憾。《小鬼迪克》近期有可能会在澳亚卫视（澳门电视台）播出，揭开长达十多年的谜团。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>小鬼迪克</li><li><span>话数: </span>26</li><li><span>放送开始: </span>1992年6月7日</li><li><span>放送星期: </span>1992年12月6日</li><li><span>别名: </span>Fairy Dick</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Hobberdy Dick</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>小精灵迪克</li><li><span>原作: </span>Katharine M. Briggs</li><li><span>企画: </span>日本瑞鹰公司</li>","collection":{"wish":8,"collect":18,"on_hold":3,"dropped":3},"tags":[{"name":"童年","count":5},{"name":"小神龙俱乐部","count":4},{"name":"欧美","count":2},{"name":"1992","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":445123,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/445123","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":445124,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/445124","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":445125,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/445125","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":445126,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/445126","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":445127,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/445127","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":445128,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/445128","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status"